            <description><![CDATA[<h1>Dictate Anywhere 2.1</h1>
<ul>
<li>Added optional Ollama-based transcript post-processing for local AI cleanup after dictation.</li>
<li>Added an AI post-processing settings screen with model refresh, download, delete, and server status checks.</li>
<li>Added reasoning controls, a custom cleanup prompt, and protected vocabulary terms for better transcript normalization.</li>
<li>Improved local AI and transcription reliability with dependency upgrades and stability fixes.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
